So we're enabling DMA when the command is an FD_DIR_READ command and the
dma_mode is VERIFY. Those read commands are:

READ
READ TRACK
READ DELETED DATA

>              break;
>          case FD_DIR_VERIFY:
>              dma_mode_ok =3D true;
> @@ -1835,8 +1836,11 @@ static int fdctrl_transfer_handler (void *opaque, =
int nchan,
